out using the Z table .

Lower CI = 520 - 1.96 * 100 / root(25) = 480.6
Higher CI = 520 + 1.96 * 100 / root(25) = 559.2

Based on the above stats we can say that , i am 95% sure that the avg CAT exam score will lie between 480 and 560 .


